        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         To date, the company has been laser-focused on financial fraud. The product works well, and each logo it adds in the space makes it easier to acquire the next similar customer. But it\xe2\x80\x99s starting to attract notice beyond that tight-knit ecosystem:
        </p>
        <ul style="margin: 1em 0;">
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
