           The World Economic Forum
           <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUbtuhDAQ_JpzB_KTR-HiilydIlFK5MceWAc2sk0Qfx_DFZGsHWlX65mdMSrDGOIh15AyOsuQjxWkhz3NkDNEtCWIg7OSNLRjgvfISm5JJzrk0vCMAItys8xxA7RuenZGZRf8tYExFWiSmEFLoO0pCMz6J2tIozR_ctFgDYrxN6_arANvQMIvxCN4QLOccl7Tjd1v9FHevu-13pLzkNLuItQmLKV9ai0whQUKUEwJbojAWDDelwb4Ur69y5RU911FC7ZSqfoCM_kwh_GoPotegFjpo_oJcbbVhwk-LM5UjxC3BTl5fdrijlAhBKtJTUijScs05ry1ClONW8OZ5oTwRpfjbhwvI63TplNW5nUqRVH6kHWIzo9l_JrUAvM1KLYNBZetiDwG8ErPYN-O5ncwl8fDCB5iCcwOKp9xiJZ3fcNYh98OFstZJ0jb9wQVZhvKlv8n_QNjCaMF" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
